snippet.title: Amber Heard Is A Mom?! Is It Wrong To Be Upset?
snippet.description:
Amber Heard Is A Mom?! Is It Wrong To Be Upset? Welcome to Hugging the Cactus' where we'll be posting videos about difficult topics, covering important topics like #JusticeForJohnnyDepp and #FreeBritney as well as how to keep good mental health in this social media world. 

#HuggingTheCactus #KeepGoing

To support this series, you can join our Patreon: http://patreon.com/huggingthecactus
